<!channel>: We’re prepping for Hood to Coast and the driver for the North van fell through. Does anyone know someone who might be interested in driving?
any more details <@U1HKQRLMR> (where/when/how long)?

It would be for the whole event. We would leave from Sarah’s house in NE early early on Thursday morning and would have the driver with us throughout the entire race. I mean, we could alternate who drives but would like a main driver.
I could ask about just driving for the first leg too? We have a stopover in Portland that first day, so we could always just have a driver for the first leg, but I think they wanted one for the race.
There are 4-6 hour gaps between each set of legs.
We’re fun guys. We promise.
i cant do it, but heres some more info for anyone who might be interested: <http://www.hoodtocoastrelay.com/race-information>
